        "subject": "LU-1415 tests: Basic support for ZFS-based servers",
        "message": "LU-1415 tests: Basic support for ZFS-based servers\n\nThis patch extends Test Framework to support formatting and mounting\nZFS-based servers.\n\n  - Global and target-type-specific FSTYPEs\n  - Format options\n    - \"--vdev-size\"\n    - \"--index\"\n  - Mount options\n    - \"-o loop\"\n  - Labels\n  - Device and VDev names\n\nThe majority of this patch was originally developed by Brian Behlendorf\nunder ORI-155.  See http://review.whamcloud.com/1417.\n\nChange-Id: I7e7c57543c1b1827c27191aac78e72f18211df18\nWhamcloud-bug-id: ORI-155\nSigned-off-by: Li Wei <liwei@whamcloud.com>\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/b2_1"
    }
